Pour @water{2%quarts} into a lidded #3 qt saucepan{} and bring to a boil over high heat.

Carefully lower @large eggs{1-6} into the water and cook for ~{30%seconds}.

Add @ice cubes{12} and allow the water to return to a boil.

Reduce to a sub-simmer, about 190Â°F. Cook for ~{11%minutes}. Drain the eggs and peel under cool running water.
